Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes have been\Nfollowing me, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! Take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was only a dream... but I was\NFINALLY going to make it with Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what their excuse is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Summer Vacation Rules! Totally Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Master Wataru is not in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call back in about 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Watura Morooka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, it's me! Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuya? Don't you know it's\Nsummer vacation, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling me before noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Kazuya Sakagami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it's a matter of\Nlife and death that we talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck. I'm already\Non my way to see Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Mai Sakuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chill out! Can we talk\Nafter you do Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Kenji Aihara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, whatever! I've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget! Be at the station, 11:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Kurumi Nishina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Production:\NPink Pineapple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Sakimake\NSenior\NHigh\NScool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:02:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Planning Producers:\NDr. Pochi\NYuta Amauti\NYoshiro Asaga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Originally created by\NMasato Hiruda (elf)\NScreenplay:\NYuhiro Tomita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Original Character\NConcepts:\NMasaki Takei\NCharacter Design/Art Direction:\NRyunosuke Otonashi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Visual Art Director:\NMasayoshi Kanemura\NDirector of Photography:\NMitsunobo Yoshida
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Satomi Kurokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, today's Kurumi's birthday!\NNo wonder he's so stressed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Satomi... What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the..?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru! Are you here to fantasize\Nabout the girls again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Misa Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Music:\NTomas Unit\NSound Effects Direction:\NYasunori Honda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staring at girls like that is\Nthe sickest thing a man can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you ran your laps stark naked,\NMisa, no one would watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're too pumped up...\Nlike a bodybuilder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know the entire\Ntrack team calls me "Bambi"\Nfor my grace and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bambi, eh? That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru! Make sure you write her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Miho Suzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho. And don't play any games\Nwith her, she's naive enough\Nto actually care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Executive Director:\NKenji Yoshimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just too generous\Nwith my affections.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is... such a tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whereas Mai is so cute and feminine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it takes, I'm going to\Nget her by the end of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show em what you got, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru Morooka!\NGet your filthy mind off of Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's perfection, the Madonna of this\NEducational Institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could ever\Nmeasure up to her standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stupid to dream about\Nsomething you'll never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about her, you'll only make\Nyourself miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, where do you\Nget off saying shit like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say it because I'm more important\Nto Mai tnan you'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll find out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♥ Wataru! ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♥ ♥ Wataru! ♥ ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♥ ♥ ♥ Wataru! ♥ ♥ ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could you make me up about\Nthirty dollars worth of flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred dollars\Nwould be even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the price of being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I've worked my\Nass off all summer to support YOU?\NThat money was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make a "wonderful summer\Nmemory" with Mai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juggling girls is asking for trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Mai is just a pampered,\Nsimpering little ditz...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who's utterly and completely\Nincompatible with you, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only make yourself miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure! I haven't noticed you\Nscoring with Kurumi, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this is all about!\NToday's Kurumi's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new plan of attack:\N"Presents for Pussy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I owe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much for such service!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you, Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing your scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My letter... Have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta Dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed that I'm going to\Nhave to send you a letter in reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuya, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kazuya! Thank you wery much!\NIt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... wasn't it awfully expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I need to give you back\Nsomething...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it! How about\Na kiss for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we can get on\Nto some serious sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're such a kidder, Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You butthead! You left me to die\Nout there in the sun, Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuya's into ropes and candles. Watch\Nyourself or you might get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes I like to play\Naround with candles too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, women don't like men\Nwho can't make up their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In her usual bitchy mood, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's related to you, but I can't\Nbelieve you let Satomi work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given my lifestyle, she's as close to a\Ndaughter as I'm ever likely to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really does try. Eventually, I'd like\Nher to take over the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, if you put Satomi\Nat the helm, this place will sink\Nlike a ship full of bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each and every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bitch! She just can't wait\Nto pick a fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... You like that Mai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. She's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got your work\Ncut out for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, doesn't she like that Kenji guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that jerk's nothing special to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you doing\Nat the school this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. You're jealous\Nabout me and Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to make something happen,\Nbefore I lose my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that kind of book?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes. For my exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go out on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I have to go to my club...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then there's my piano class...\NAnd other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying! God give me strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi did... Kurumi didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired! Kazuya's whining\Nkept me up half the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And worse, I'm not sure leaving her\Nat the hotel like that was justified,\Njust because she said no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like someone beat me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji and Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Your parents told you\Nnot to run anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They want me to quit\Nthe track club and concentrate\Non my college exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is your last year of high\Nschool, after all... I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, maybe they think\Nthat if you quit the team\Nyou'd become more feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so lucky. All it takes to make\Nyou happy is a girl to chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, can you imagine what it would\Nbe like for me, not running anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started when I was in 6th grade, and\NI've got one chance left at the nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to keep running.\NUntil the nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on running. Don't worry\Nabout what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to do what's right for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A "Thank You" from HER mouth?\NNow THAT'S weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Wataru, this is so embarrassing,\Nbut I'm going to write it anyway."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Could you please take... please take\NMiho to a movie... please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I would like to see something with a\Nlove story. I'll be waiting for your reply."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho could you tone it down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!          Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do to Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... well... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho was crying her head off\Nwhen she called me last night!\NWhat did you DO to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, when you think about it, I'm\Nthe one who should be crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You're thinking more of your\Nperverted thoughts, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho is not the kind of tramp\Nyou normally go out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make her cry again\Nyou're going to answer to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all the girls around\Nhere, isn't there one you\Nreally find the most attractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the prettiest, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come have chocolate patties with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you're going out with Kenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that. It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All a man needs is\Nthe proper disposition\Nand his strength of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like money and status don't\Nmatter, isn't that correct, Lady Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru is forged of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from a novel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He leapt over the dying flames, then,\Nthe final barrier behind him..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...he stood at last, Body and Soul,\Nbeside her."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...her heaving breasts caressed the\Nmanly expanse of his chest..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This sensation! He thought..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This was what he had dreamed of with\Neach magnificent ripple of the glories\Nbeneath her taut sweater!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you yearning for\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a South Sea island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an amusement park in Yabuki\Nthat's just opened a waterpark with a\NSouth Sea Island theme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a whirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you, this Friday,\Nat one o'clock at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a piano lesson that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deal. This Friday, at the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess with some girls\Nit just pays to be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We can come\Nback for your bike later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're humiliating me! Let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!!! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only make it worse\Nif you won't hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to run anymore!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nationals are coming soon.\NYou've got to take care of your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone ever tell you\Nyou've got really big breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asshole! Pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wouldn't listen, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The injury to your knee is the direct\Nresult of excessive training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to have surgery now,\Notherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being stubborn. The doctor's\Ninsisting because she cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, you've run enough. Let's\Njust fix your leg and concentrate\Non your entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tripped during my morning run.\NPretty stupid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Mako told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so stupid. I'll never run again\Nbecause I ran too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Wataru... you were the\Nonly one to back me up, to say\N"do what's right for you".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess now I can be the girl my\Nparents want me to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that! Everybody's\Nbeen worried sick about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if they fix it right, surely\Nyou'll be able to run again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody keeps saying that.\NBut this was my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ignored the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time... now everyone knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Misa... but so many\Npeople care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, even I miss having good old\NMisa keeping me in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up. Even if you can't run\Nanymore, that doesn't mean\Nanything else would change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are my muscles too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just built firm... and very lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting fed up with\NKurumi acting like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because the only\Nmature thing you're interested\Nin is screwing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what do you suggest I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being honest about your\Nfeelings wouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be nice to square\Neverything with Kurumi? Maybe\Nyou'd even finally get laid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard the worst of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now her father's gotten into the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day he got on my case,\Nyelling "What are you doing\Nto my daughter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've made a decision.\NKurumi and I are through!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm changing my focus to older\Nmore mature women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! Can I have a go at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi and Kenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.47,0:24:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mai isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.47,0:24:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's Mai? Is she\Nsick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.91,0:24:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be seeing her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you talking about?\NMai and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.02,0:24:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, what's the deal\Nwith you and Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.42,0:24:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.89,0:25:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Mai is no\Nlonger available, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, where's Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called in sick. Took the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. She's never\Ndone that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me... don't you think Satomi's\Nbeen acting a little odd lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her temper gets the better of her,\Nshe drops dishes... She just acts\Nlike she's feeling down...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day she even spilled\Ncoffee all over a customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.82,0:25:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.99,0:25:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swear to God! You don't have\Nany idea what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.34,0:25:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.64,0:25:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't. It's not my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.98,0:25:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... But I'm so very worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.12,0:25:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.65,0:25:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.43,0:26:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think Kazuya's\Nbeen avoiding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.58,0:26:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is that something\Nworth crying over?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.81,0:26:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the last few times we were\Ntogether, it was like he didn't\Nhear a word I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.31,0:26:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now, when I call, he always\Nsays he's busy and refuses to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.19,0:26:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot. I guess\Nhe was really serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.79,0:26:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my fault... when I\Nrejected him at the hotel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.07,0:26:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that could have\Nsomething to do with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.07,0:26:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean no! I was only joking, Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.64,0:26:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kazuya were\Nmade for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.37,0:26:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep smiling at him, Kurumi, and\Neverything will turn out okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.15,0:27:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.08,0:27:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.55,0:27:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll trust Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, that's swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.64,0:27:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men and women... Why do they\Nhave to be such opposites?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.11,0:27:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I don't\Nhave problems like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.61,0:27:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.17,0:27:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:27:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?\NYou look a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.38,0:28:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.75,0:28:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.69,0:28:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I saw you\Nand Kenji at a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.66,0:28:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.46,0:28:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I just ran into him in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.50,0:28:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.37,0:29:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a little early.\NMaybe I can kill some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.21,0:29:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.78,0:29:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.12,0:29:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Satomi anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi? No, not recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.06,0:29:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't show up for work again,\Nso I called her house...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and her mother said\Nshe'd left for work hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.26,0:29:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so terribly worried. I just pray she's\Nall right! Please, help me find Satomi\Nbefore something terrible happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.73,0:29:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.03,0:29:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm begging you, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.58,0:29:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.04,0:31:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi? No, I haven't seen her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.44,0:31:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.67,0:31:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako, did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.11,0:31:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.65,0:31:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Nothing. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.39,0:32:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, Master's worried sick about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.23,0:32:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least give him a call...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.58,0:32:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, I know it's none\Nof my business but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.12,0:32:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.69,0:32:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.16,0:32:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.66,0:32:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I just want to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.86,0:32:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Made it, just in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.99,0:33:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, girls DO take a bit\Nof time to prepare...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.03,0:33:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I gave her the\Nwrong time to meet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.21,0:34:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Sakuragi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.58,0:34:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, My name is Morooka.\NIs Mai there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Mai has decided not to see\Nanyone until the new semester begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to talk to her.\NHave a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.06,0:34:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What??
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.76,0:34:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.81,0:34:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.91,0:35:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.38,0:35:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.15,0:35:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.27,0:36:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell???
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.11,0:36:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, Master Wataru is out.\NIf you have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.15,0:36:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.02,0:36:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.02,0:36:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.29,0:36:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything today.\NI appreciate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.36,0:36:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.70,0:36:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.17,0:36:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.61,0:36:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.32,0:37:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.26,0:37:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.06,0:37:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I never thought\Nyou'd be so worried about me.\NIt's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.30,0:37:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah... Did you call Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.64,0:37:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worried so many people,\Ndidn't I? I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.58,0:37:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... about Kenji... he dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.09,0:37:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really in love...\Nbut he told me it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji's... already seeing another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.70,0:37:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another... girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.11,0:38:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me! Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.94,0:38:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Make me forget about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.35,0:38:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.55,0:38:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only... With you it would be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.09,0:38:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make love to me, Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.17,0:38:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful, Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.81,0:38:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.01,0:38:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.07,0:39:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.53,0:39:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.91,0:39:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... again... again...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.82,0:40:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.39,0:40:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, come to me, Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.12,0:40:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.29,0:41:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... Wataru... more...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.95,0:41:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi... I'm coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.86,0:41:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I'm coming. I'm coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.08,0:42:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.75,0:42:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.22,0:42:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I can't wait to\Nget back to your shop and have\Na cup of that great coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.53,0:42:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Wataru...
